      <p class="headline">OVERVIEW</p>
      <h2>"There's an app?"</h2>
      <div></div>
      <p>
        Anime Revolution's app relaunched in 2023. There is hardly any
        recognition for it currently, due to low visibility of product as well
        as because its use case scenario was isolated from the actual user
        experience thus far.
      </p>
